        <h3>What is CodeBook ?</h3>
        <p class="my_font">It's an Online Compiler and interpreter which runs your code on the Web, plus with CodeBook you can save all of your executed programs safe in your Account and can revisit and rerun them anytime.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card" data-aos="fade-right">
      <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/04/20/13/17/work-731198__340.jpg" alt="" srcset="">
      <div>
        <h3>Why CodeBook ?</h3>
        <p class="my_font">Programming is a Fun thing to do, but before we start to program first thing that we need to set is our coding environment which differs for all programming language, and in doing so we waste much of our time.
          But with CodeBook, you do not have to care, all you need is to get started.
          CodeBook, is all in one Compiler/Interpreter for four programming languages namely C, C++, Java and Python 
          </p>
      </div>
    </section>


